<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.3.5">
<l>palapala nāḻañcollip paḻittacicu pālaṉtaṉṉai</l>
<l>yalavalai maitavirtta vaḻakaṉalaṅ kāraṉmalai</l>
<l>kulamalai kōlamalai kuḷirmāmalai koṟṟamalai</l>
<l>nilamalai nīṇṭamalai tirumāliruñ cōlaiyatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain of the ornamented lord, the handsome one,</l>
<l rend="indent">who stopped the babbling of Śiśupāla who ridiculed [him],</l>
<l rend="indent">uttering many, many abuses,</l>
<l>that is Tirumāliruñcōlai, the noble mountain, </l>
<l rend="indent">the beautiful mountain, the huge, cool mountain,</l>
<l rend="indent">the victory mountain, the earth mountain,</l>
<l rend="indent">the tall mountain.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
